Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to Kyros and Rebecca?
