Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very intense fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even feel it through my Clairvoyance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Kyros' pain and anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't dropped dead yet?!\NYou monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've reached your limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the iron balls stopped raining down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off myself \Nto end this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Scarlet that you two loved so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante! What a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mentioned Sister-{\i1}sama{\i0} again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry! King Riku-sama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our desperate search ended in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man named Diamante was ahead of us and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Scarlet-{\i1}sama{\i0} was found in the town and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...got shot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You killed Sister-sama?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she was your older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was buying food at a market in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she could've controlled her hunger,\Nshe didn't have to die! What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't jump the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay in the Palace, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let any of you survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys lost to us a decade ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losers should accept their lot\Nand face their demise miserably!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strike will rend even the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can dodge it\Nwith your one leg that's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't dodge, you're just an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all my heart and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword carries a decade worth \Nof pain that this country suffered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take back peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half Moon Glaive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you! Robiland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you need to get treatment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I couldn't protect your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna protect you to the end,\Nwith my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day you are filled with happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Army Commander Kyros got...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took down Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took down the formidable Diamante?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Brother Kyros won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca is okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin protected her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he took \Ndown the top executive of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Donquixote Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took down the hero of the Colosseum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros was the original undefeated hero\Nof the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought no one can beat the \NDonquixote Family but they've
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been taken down one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Army Commander Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Se√±or Pink at the factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the other executives have been \Nbrought down by the warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who side with Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:19:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four major fighters of\Nthe Donquixote Family left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy the Hyena and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...two top executives - Pica and Trebol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the current king, one of the Seven \NWarlords of the Sea, Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four of them left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect them to make it that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're amazing! The Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we were trying to save ourselves\Nby killing those great people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like they say, we all make mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand it now, it's okay!\NI'll forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man King Riku, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone will try to kill me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go down to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there is still something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna depend on\Nthe Government or the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's feeling hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think they can't get away from\Nthis Birdcage and this deadly game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tell everybody in the town\Nthat there is hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are turning in our favor, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the Navy admiral go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went down a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The capture of those running \Nout of control is going well
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we haven't taken care of everything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather all the citizens in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within a defensible perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ripple!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower Climb Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do now.\NThis is it for our fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You can't just do as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, it's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the one that Zoro was keeping off! Pica!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A top executive of the Family shouldn't \Nlook so pathetic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pica tears up his tough opponents \None after another with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:29.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,his tremendous power and Zoro \Nstands to challenge him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That, however, was Pica's grand trap!\NLeaving Zoro stranded in a distant place,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pica treads on the ground and begins a major
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:40.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,counterattack to eliminate King Riku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moving Across the Ground!\NThe Giant Statue Pica's Surprise Maneuver!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
